{
  "stem": "17526.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 98.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is number A-33.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was tattooed in Blechhammer-- and it was at the beginning of 1943, when Blechhammer was taken over by the SS, and it became a concentration camp, whereas before it was a-- an arbeitslager, a work camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was the 33rd in line.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This does not indicate in any way that I was the 33rd when they started tattooing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tattooed from one to 200,000, six digits, and down they started with series A, which went to 20,000.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after 20,000, they started with series B.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At first, when they tattooed, they put the people out by their-- by their letter, alphabetically.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when they came to series A, they just rounded us up, stood in the line.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A cousin of mine that lives in Jerusalem, he has A-14.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, there's very few left with these numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But everywhere I go, even among our own people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ironically, I met a guy last week who was in the same camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, how come you have such a small number?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know you were in the same camp as I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, he was in camp there before when I came from the other camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, this is-- I was at 33rd in line so I have A-33.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- all these years since the liberation, I could not see why one would want to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ridiculed them, I-- I argued with them fiercely.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, why are you going back?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Are you going to find somebody?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Are you going to find a-- a neighbor, are you going to find a cousin, an uncle, an acquaintance, a friend that you went to school with?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What's the sense going back?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
